---
// IA Section - L'IA chez Smice
---

<section class="ia-section" id="ia">
  <div class="ia-container">
    <h2 class="ia-title">
      L'<span class="highlight-yellow">IA</span> chez Smice, évidemment.
    </h2>
    
    <div class="ia-content">
      <div class="ia-image-group">
        <div class="ia-bloc-verbatims">
          <img src="/images/homepage/ia/bloc-ia-verbatims.png" alt="Résumé de verbatims" />
        </div>
        <div class="ia-bloc-campagnes">
          <img src="/images/homepage/ia/bloc-ia-campagnes.png" alt="Création de campagnes" />
        </div>
          <div class="ia-ceo-border-group">
            <img class="ceo-border" src="/images/homepage/ia/border-ceo.png" alt="" />
            <div class="ceo-img-stack">
              <img class="ceo-border-2" src="/images/homepage/ia/border-ceo-2.png" alt="" />
              <img class="ceo-img" src="/images/homepage/ia/ceo.png" alt="CEO Smice" />
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="ia-text">
        <blockquote class="ia-quote">
          "Grâce à notre communauté, nous pouvons déployer vos programmes qualité rapidement et efficacement, quel que soit le secteur ou la localisation.
        </blockquote>
        <p class="ia-description">
          Nos profils sont soigneusement sélectionnés selon vos critères : expérience, type de mission, et zone géographique."
        </p>
        
        <div class="ia-author">
          <div class="author-avatar">
            <img src="/images/ia/julien-avatar.png" alt="Julien Mondhard" />
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <span class="author-name">Julien Mondhard</span>
            <span class="author-role">CEO - Smice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ia-section {
    background-color: #E8EDF8;
    padding: 80px 24px;
  }

  .ia-container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ia-title {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A1A2E;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 50px 0;
  }

  .ia-title .highlight-yellow {
    position: relative;
    display: inline;
  }

  .ia-title .highlight-yellow::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    bottom: 4px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background: #FFE566;
    border-radius: 4px;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .ia-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Image Section */
  .ia-image-group {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 420px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    background: #DDE3F2;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 24px 0 24px 24px;
    overflow: visible;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px 0 rgba(68, 88, 136, 0.08);
  }

  .ia-ceo-img {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    height: 370px;
    margin-left: 40px;
    margin-right: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10));
  }

    .ia-ceo-border-group {
      position: absolute;
      right: 24px;
      bottom: 0;
      height: 370px;
      width: 240px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .ia-ceo-border-group .ceo-border {
      position: absolute;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 240px;
      height: 370px;
      z-index: 3;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ia-ceo-border-group .ceo-img-stack {
      position: absolute;
      right: 18px;
      bottom: 10px;
      width: 200px;
      height: 340px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: stretch;
      justify-content: stretch;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .ia-ceo-border-group .ceo-border-2 {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 200px;
      height: 340px;
      z-index: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ia-ceo-border-group .ceo-img {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 200px;
      height: 340px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 18px;
      z-index: 1;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      background: transparent;
    }

  .ia-bloc-verbatims {
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px;
    left: 18px;
    width: 210px;
    z-index: 2;
    transform: rotate(-7deg);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  }

  .ia-bloc-campagnes {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 32px;
    left: 0px;
    width: 210px;
    z-index: 2;
    transform: rotate(-4deg);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
  }

  .frequency-badge {
    background: #4A5FC1;
    color: white;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .card-mini-text {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #6B7280;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .card-mini-text p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .card-icon {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 10px;
    right: 10px;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  /* Paper Planes */
  .paper-plane {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 24px;
    z-index: 3;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .plane-1 {
    top: 50%;
    right: 20px;
    transform: rotate(-30deg);
  }

  .plane-2 {
    bottom: 80px;
    right: 60px;
    transform: rotate(15deg);
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  /* Text Section */
  .ia-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .ia-quote {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .ia-description {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ia-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: #D1D5DB;
  }

  .author-avatar img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #4A5FC1;
  }

  .author-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #6B7280;
  }

  /* ===== Tablet Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .ia-section {
      padding: 60px 24px;
    }

    .ia-title {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .ia-content {
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .ia-image {
      min-height: 350px;
    }

    .main-image {
      max-width: 320px;
    }

    .card-verbatims {
      width: 190px;
    }

    .card-campagnes {
      width: 170px;
      left: -10px;
    }

    .ia-quote,
    .ia-description {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Mobile Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ia-section {
      padding: 50px 20px;
    }

    .ia-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
    }

    .ia-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 35px;
    }

    .ia-image {
      min-height: 320px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .main-image {
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .floating-card {
      transform: scale(0.85);
    }

    .card-verbatims {
      top: 10px;
      left: 10%;
    }

    .card-campagnes {
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 5%;
    }

    .paper-plane {
      display: none;
    }

    .ia-text {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .ia-quote,
    .ia-description {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ia-author {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Small Mobile ===== */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .ia-title {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .ia-title .highlight-yellow::after {
      height: 6px;
      bottom: 2px;
    }

    .floating-card {
      transform: scale(0.75);
    }

    .card-verbatims {
      left: 0;
    }

    .card-campagnes {
      left: 0;
    }

    .author-avatar {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
    }

    .author-name {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
